  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Katon)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> *</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You attempt to instantly heat the water inside a 5 ft cube or a target creature to a boiling point, having a Cost and effect based on the target. You can select 1 target per 5 levels, each of the same type, but you must pay the cost for each target you choose.<br><br>5 ft Cube (4 Chakra): You target a square to evaporate water from. If there is sufficient water (at least 3 inches), a burst of steam deals 6d6 fire damage in a 5ft wide, 10 ft high Cylinder (Reflex halves).<br><br>Creature (10 Chakra): You temporarily make the target's bodily fluids boil, dealing 6d6 fire damage to it and requiring it to make a Fortitude save to avoid 1d6 Constitution damage and becoming fatigued.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
